  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 18th level, you learn the ultimate molding technique for Hemomantic techniques called Sanguine Master. </p><p>When you cast a ninjutsu that deals acid, necrotic or poison damage, you can embolden the jutsu cast. </p><p>You can only use this molding by spending 10 chakra. </p><p>You can use this molding in addition to any other efficient molding you are using. </p><p>This jutsu ignores immunity, resistance and damage reduction. </p><p>Additionally, damage this jutsu deals reduces the target creature's Maximum Hit Points by the same amount for the next minute.</p>",
